(50, 'Đất đai của Bill Gates đã gần bằng Hong Kong', 'Berlin, Germany’s capital, dates to the 13th century. Reminders of the city\'s turbulent 20th-century history include its Holocaust memorial and the Berlin Wall\'s graffitied remains. Divided during the Cold War, its 18th-century Brandenburg Gate has become a symbol of reunification. The city\'s also known for its art scene and modern landmarks like the gold-colored, swoop-roofed Berliner Philharmonie, built in 1963.', 'http://localhost:8080/blog/Fileupload/post18.jpg', 41, 2, '2021-04-07 04:36:31', '2021-04-07 04:36:31'),
