(56, 'Is a Trip to Halong Chốt lời hay đổ thêm tiền mua vào khi chứng khoán lên đỉnh?', 'ays Nikki Scott of South East Asia Backpacker, “It\'s no wonder that Halong Bay is a magnet for tourists from all over the world. However, some things are popular for a reason, and Halong Bay is definitely one of them. No one can deny the unique beauty of the bay, and depending on which cruise you choose, it is possible to have a relaxing and memorable experience that isn\'t ruined by a bucket-load of tourists.  While I am often in favor of independent travel over organized tours, Halong Bay is one of those places that cannot be experienced without booking some kind of group tour. (Unless you have your own sailboat, that is!) It\'s important to know that the tour you choose will greatly affect the type of experience that you have – so choose wisely. If you don\'t want to end up singing karaoke at 4am on a boat decked out with neon lights and a disco ball, then be sure to do your research!“', 'http://localhost:8080/blog/Fileupload/post20.jpg', 41, 19, '2021-04-07 04:36:54', '2021-04-07 04:36:54'),
