(69, 'The 10 Most Beautiful Beach Destinations In Vietnam', 'Boasting some 2,000 miles of coastline plus a handful of renowned island destinations, Vietnam naturally has no shortage of beautiful beaches. Sure, you could just stick to cities, what with the colonial architecture and history of Hanoi, the imperial charms of Hue, and the bustling nightlife of Saigon. But you\'d be remiss to plan a Vietnamese vacation without hitting the water at least once—plus, most cities are just a day-trip from the coast, if not on the coast already.', 'http://localhost:8080/blog/Fileupload/beach2.jpg', 41, 19, '2021-04-07 10:11:06', '2021-04-07 10:11:06'),
